msgid "0:ひとつの実験が、あった。[%p]"
msgstr "0:An experiment had been performed.[%p]"

msgid "100:だが、それを“彼女”が知ることはなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "100:But she never knew.[%p]"

msgid "200:“彼女”は、４０歳を前に第二子を授かった、ごく普通の専業主婦だった。[%p]"
msgstr "200:She was a normal housewife, close to turning 40, newly pregnant with her second child.[%p]"

msgid "300:いや、ごく普通、ではないかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "300:No, maybe she wasn't quite normal.[%p]"

msgid "400:なにしろ長女はもう高校生になろうという年齢であり、第二子と１５歳近い隔たりがあるのだ。[%p]"
msgstr "400:Her first daughter was already only a year away from high school, so there would be an almost fifteen-year gap between her children.[%p]"

msgid "500:そのことで思春期の長女がなんらかの抵抗を感じてしまうのではないかと少し心配したが、逆に長女は“彼女”の妊娠を心から喜んでくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "500:She was worried that her daughter, who was currently going through puberty, would rebel against having a younger sister. But in fact, her daughter was overjoyed.[%p]"

msgid "600:科学者の夫は、研究と信仰に没頭してほとんど家には帰ってこないが、家ではよき夫であろうとしてくれたし、よき父親であろうとしてくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "600:Her husband was a scientist, and between his faith and his research, only rarely came home. But whenever he was home, he did his best to be a good father and a good husband.[%p]"

msgid "700:だから“彼女”としては、不満は多少あるものの、夫への愛は揺るがなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "700:So, while she certainly had her complaints, her love for her husband was firm.[%p]"

msgid "800:第二子は無事に産まれた。[linebreak]２５７９グラムの元気な女の子だった。[%p]"
msgstr "800:The second child was born uneventfully. She was a healthy young girl, who weighed 2,579 grams at birth.[%p]"

msgid "900:“彼女”はその子をマナと名付けた。[%p]"
msgstr "900:She named the girl Mana.[%p]"

msgid "1000:その直後に、残念なことに夫の単身赴任が決まった。[%p]"
msgstr "1000:Unfortunately, after that, her husband was transferred to a new location far away from home.[%p]"

msgid "1100:夫には一般的な生活能力が皆無だったから、しっかり者の長女に、父親に付いていって世話をするよう頼まなければならなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "1100:Her husband wouldn't last a week without someone to do the chores and make the food, so she had no choice but to send her older daughter along with him.[%p]"

msgid "1200:生まれたばかりのマナと２人だけで生活することになった“彼女”は、夫の提案で格安の社宅に転居することになった。[%p]"
msgstr "1200:She was now alone with her newborn daughter Mana. At her husband's suggestion, the two of them moved into housing owned by the company he worked for, so rent was extremely low.[%p]"

msgid "1300:もともと“彼女”の一家は郊外のマンションに住んでいたが、交通の便が悪いところにあった。[%p]"
msgstr "1300:Her family had originally lived in a condo in the suburbs, but it was far from the city center and hard to get anywhere.[%p]"

msgid "1400:だが新たに住むことになる社宅は、渋谷の一等地にあり、隣近所には夫の同僚家族も多く住んでいる。育児も含めいざというときに困ることもないだろう、という夫の配慮だった。[%p]"
msgstr "1400:The dorm, however, was located right in heart of Shibuya, and many of her husband's colleagues lived nearby. She'd have easy access to childcare, and if anything came up, she'd have people around who could help her.[%p]"

msgid "1500:社宅はどの部屋も広く、特に寝室が“彼女”のお気に入りになった。[%p]"
msgstr "1500:The place was extremely spacious. The bedroom, especially, was a favorite of hers.[%p]"

msgid "1600:壁一面に大きな鏡があり、反対側の壁にはこれまた大きな窓。そこから、代々木公園の緑を眺めることができた。[%p]"
msgstr "1600:A huge mirror covered a whole wall, and on the other side, there was a big window. From there, you could look down onto Yoyogi Park.[%p]"

msgid "1700:すぐに隣に住む婦人とも友達になり、さらには会社からの破格の待遇により、家政婦を付けてもらえることになった。[%p]"
msgstr "1700:She quickly became friends with the ladies in the nearby residences, and the corporate benefits even included a maid.[%p]"

msgid "1800:それだけ、夫は会社の中で重要なポジションにいるのだ、という誇らしい気持ちもあって、“彼女”はこのなに不自由ない生活に満足していた。[%p]"
msgstr "1800:She was proud that her husband was important enough in the company for her to have all these benefits, and was more than satisfied with her life of luxury.[%p]"

msgid "1900:そして２年。[linebreak]マナは、少し成長が遅れているもののこれまで大きな病気をすることもなく元気に育っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "1900:Two years passed. Mana's development was a little slow, but she was growing up without suffering any major illnesses.[%p]"

msgid "2000:とても甘えん坊屋さんだった。[%p]"
msgstr "2000:She was, however, a very needy child.[%p]"

msgid "2100:常に“彼女”が胸に抱いておいてやらないと、けたたましく泣き始めてしまうのだ。[%p]"
msgstr "2100:If she wasn't constantly held at her mother's breast, she'd start crying immediately.[%p]"

msgid "2200:“彼女”自身はここ１ヶ月ほど体調を崩していた。特に耳鳴りがひどく、ほぼ一日中それに悩まされていた。[%p]"
msgstr "2200:For the past month or so, Mana's mother hadn't been feeling well at all. The ringing in her ears was the worst part. It bothered her almost the whole day.[%p]"

msgid "2300:それでも、マナの世話は家政婦さんや隣の婦人には任せられなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "2300:But still, she couldn't let the maid or the lady next door take care of Mana.[%p]"

msgid "2400:とにかくマナは“彼女”にベッタリで、片時も離れようとしなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "2400:Mana couldn't stand to be away from her for a second.[%p]"

msgid "2500:トイレに行くときも、お風呂に入るときも。[%p]"
msgstr "2500:Not in the bathroom. Not when taking a bath.[%p]"

msgid "2600:家政婦さんに少しだけ抱いていてもらおうと思っても、“彼女”がそうしようかと考えていることを敏感に察知し、泣き出してしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "2600:Whenever she even thought of letting the maid hold her for a second, Mana would somehow know, and start crying.[%p]"

msgid "2700:逆にそれだけ“彼女”を頼っているということに愛おしさも感じたが、おかげで“彼女”は家から一歩も出ることができない生活が続いた。[%p]"
msgstr "2700:It was, in a way, endearing to have the young child so reliant on her, but it also meant that she couldn't leave the house for an instant.[%p]"

msgid "2800:家政婦と婦人がそんな“彼女”の生活を支えてくれた。[linebreak]２人と出会えたことは、“彼女”にとっては本当に救いになった。[%p]"
msgstr "2800:The maid and her neighbor, though, were there to help. She was so lucky to have met them.[%p]"

msgid "2900:もっとも、その２人の様子も徐々におかしくなっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "2900:Of course, things were gradually getting strange with them, too.[%p]"

msgid "3000:１週間前、リビングでお喋りをしていたら、なんの前触れもなく婦人が嘔吐した。驚く“彼女”をよそに、婦人は外へと飛び出していった。[%p]"
msgstr "3000:A week ago, she'd been talking with her neighbor in the living room, when the woman had suddenly started to vomit without warning. She'd quickly fled afterward, running outside of the house.[%p]"

msgid "3100:それ以来顔を合わせられないでいたので、もしかしたら病気にでもなったのかもしれない、と“彼女”は心配した。[%p]"
msgstr "3100:Mana's mother hadn't seen the neighbor at all after that, so perhaps she'd gotten sick.[%p]"

msgid "3200:そこで“彼女”は、婦人の様子を見てきてほしいと家政婦に頼むことにした。[%p]"
msgstr "3200:Mana's mother then decided to ask her maid to go check on the neighbor.[%p]"

msgid "3300:仕事を終えて帰ろうとしていた家政婦にそれを告げ、[linebreak]“明日もお願いね”と言ったら、家政婦は突然泣き出し、[linebreak]何度もうなずきながら帰っていった。[%p]"
msgstr "3300:The maid was just finishing up for the day when she'd made the request. When she'd finished it with, “And I'll see you tomorrow,” the maid suddenly began to cry. The maid just nodded over and over again, before leaving.[%p]"

msgid "3400:その夜、“彼女”をずっと苛んでいた耳鳴りが激しくなり、頭が割れんばかりの痛みが走った。[%p]"
msgstr "3400:And that night, Mana's mother suffered terribly as the ringing in her ears got even more violent than before, and the pain threatened to split her head open.[%p]"

msgid "3500:救急車を呼ぼうとしたが、電話が通じなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "3500:She tried to call an ambulance, but the phones didn't work.[%p]"

msgid "3600:外に出て、隣の婦人に助けを求めようとしたが、それさえも困難なほどだった。[%p]"
msgstr "3600:She tried to go get the neighbor lady to help, but even that was too difficult.[%p]"

msgid "3700:娘が激しく泣き、その声にまた痛みが刺激された。[%p]"
msgstr "3700:Her daughter started to cry violently, and the crying made the pain worse.[%p]"

msgid "3800:必死でマナをかき抱き、痛みに耐えていたら。[linebreak]"
msgstr "3800:She held Mana tight to her chest, enduring the pain.[linebreak]"

msgid "3900:唐突に、耳鳴りと、泣き声がやんだ。[linebreak]頭の痛みも、嘘のように引いていた。[%p]"
msgstr "3900:Suddenly the crying and the ringing in her ears stopped. The pain in her head was gone, like it had never been there.[%p]"

msgid "4000:必死でマナをかき抱き、痛みに耐えていたら。唐突に、耳鳴りと、泣き声がやんだ。頭の痛みも、嘘のように引いていた。"
msgstr "4000:She held Mana tight to her chest, enduring the pain. Suddenly the crying and the ringing in her ears stopped. The pain in her head was gone, like it had never been there."

msgid "4100:ふと見ると[linebreak]"
msgstr "4100:She looked down, and saw she was holding the shriveled[linebreak]"

msgid "4200:“彼女”の抱いていた子がミイラになっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "4200:corpse of a child.[%p]"

msgid "4300:ふと見ると“彼女”の抱いていた子がミイラになっていた。"
msgstr "4300:She looked down, and saw she was holding the shriveled corpse of a child."

msgid "4400:それが実験だったと気付く前に、[unk07 unk="60"]“彼女”の心は壊れた。[%p]"
msgstr "4400:Before she realized that the whole thing was an experiment,[unk07 unk="60"] her mind broke into a million pieces.[%p]"

msgid "4500:ひとつの実験が、あった。[%p]"
msgstr "4500:An experiment had been performed.[%p]"

msgid "4600:だが、それは“彼”が想定していたものとは違っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "4600:But it wasn't what he had expected it to be.[%p]"

msgid "4700:“彼”は、希テクノロジー社の科学者。天成神光会の信者。希テクノロジー社が極秘裏に行っていたプロジェクト・ノアの中心人物であり、ｆｕｎ＾１０×ｉｎｔ＾４０ = Ｉｒ２について解読した男でもあった。[%p]"
msgstr "4700:He was a scientist at Nozomi Technologies, and a believer in the Cosmic Church of the Divine Light. He was one of the key figures behind Nozomi Tech's secret Project Noah, and the one who'd solved the riddle of fun^10xint^40=Ir2.[%p]"

msgid "4800:“彼”は実験のために、出産間際の妻を被験者として差し出した。それは彼が崇める教祖からの指示であると同時に、彼自身が実験を成功させるために自ら言い出したことでもあった。[%p]"
msgstr "4800:He had offered his pregnant wife as a test subject for the experiment. It was a direct order from the church's leader, a person he admired deeply. But he had also been the one to suggest it, to make the experiment a success.[%p]"

msgid "4900:その実験は、妻が産んだ次女に付けられたコードネームから、マナ実験と呼ばれた。[%p]"
msgstr "4900:It was called the Mana Experiment, after the codename given to his wife's daughter.[%p]"

msgid "5000:当時１５歳になっていた長女は天成神光会の施設で預かってもらい、“彼”は、幽閉した妻とマナを２４時間付きっきりで観察した。[%p]"
msgstr "5000:His older daughter was given to a church facility, while he monitored his sequestered wife and Mana twenty-four hours a day.[%p]"

msgid "5100:妻が会社の社宅だと思いこんでいた部屋は、希テクノロジーが用意した実験場であり、そこには“彼”が開発中のノアⅡプロトタイプが配置されていた。[%p]"
msgstr "5100:What his wife had thought was a company-owned condo was, in fact, a Nozomi Technologies testing facility, and the location of the Noah II prototype that he was working on.[%p]"

msgid "5200:思考盗撮、視覚投影、五感制御。それらの効果を、実験場に閉じこめた妻やマナへの人体実験によって確かめる。[%p]"
msgstr "5200:Mind-reading. Induced hallucinations. Sensory control. His wife and daughter would be used to test the efficacy of these technologies, here in this sealed lab.[%p]"

msgid "5300:電磁の力が人体に与える影響は未知数で、当然ながら“彼”は、妻やマナの身体に異変が生じればすぐ実験を中止する予定だった。[%p]"
msgstr "5300:The effects of electromagnetic radiation on the body were ill-understood, and he had planned to cancel the experiments if anything unusual happened to his wife and daughter.[%p]"

msgid "5400:実験は、開始早々にアクシデントに見舞われた。[%p]"
msgstr "5400:An accident occurred almost immediately.[%p]"

msgid "5500:マナが、生後わずか１ヶ月で死んだ。死因は分からなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "5500:Mana died roughly a month after being born. The cause of her death was unknown.[%p]"

msgid "5600:誰にも、防ぐことはできないアクシデントだった。[%p]"
msgstr "5600:It was an accident, one that nobody could prevent.[%p]"

msgid "5700:“彼”は悲嘆に暮れ、実験を中止させようとした。[linebreak]だがそれは許されなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "5700:He was deeply saddened, and tried to cancel the experiment. But that wasn't going to happen.[%p]"

msgid "5800:[name]野呂瀬[line]「実に興味深いではないですか」[%p]"
msgstr "5800:[name]野呂瀬[line]It's quite interesting, don't you think?[%p]"

msgid "5900:“彼”の雇い主はそう言った。[%p]"
msgstr "5900:That's what his employer had said.[%p]"

msgid "6000:実験場内の異様な光景のことを雇い主は言っていたのだった。[%p]"
msgstr "6000:The man had been looking at the strange goings-on in the test lab.[%p]"

msgid "6100:妻は、マナの死を現実として認めようとせず、亡骸となった子供をまるで生きているように扱った。実際、妻の目にはマナは生きていると映っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "6100:His wife had refused to accept the reality of her daughter's death, and treated her corpse like it was still alive. In fact, from his wife's perspective, she was.[%p]"

msgid "6200:それはノアⅡプロトタイプによる影響であり、ある意味でその性能を確かめるには絶好の状況だった。[%p]"
msgstr "6200:This was an effect of the Noah II prototype, and in a sense, the perfect chance to test its abilities.[%p]"

msgid "6300:“彼”の意志は黙殺された。[%p]"
msgstr "6300:His feelings on the matter were irrelevant.[%p]"

msgid "6400:やがて“彼”もまた、このまま実験を続ける方が妻のためにいいのではないかと思うようになった。[%p]"
msgstr "6400:And before long, he too began to feel that his wife would be better off if the experiment continued.[%p]"

msgid "6500:マジックミラー越しに眺める妻は、子供の死体を抱きながらも、毎日幸せそうに暮らしていた。[%p]"
msgstr "6500:As he watched his wife through the one-way mirror, cradling his daughter's corpse, it seemed like she was happy with her life.[%p]"

msgid "6600:壁に張られた“窓のように見える壁紙”から、視覚投影されたフェイクの代々木公園の緑を眺め、子供に優しく語りかけていた。[%p]"
msgstr "6600:She'd stare at the wallpaper on the opposite site, which looked to her like a window overlooking Yoyogi Park, and whisper softly to her daughter.[%p]"

msgid "6700:“隣の婦人”および“家政婦”に扮した研究チームのスタッフが妻の世話をしてくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "6700:Two of the research staff took care of her. One would pretend to be a maid, the other, the lady next door.[%p]"

msgid "6800:実験が続く限り、妻の心が壊れてしまうことはない。[linebreak]これが妻のためなのだと自分に言い聞かせた。[%p]"
msgstr "6800:As long as the experiment continued, his wife's mind would be just fine. This was, he told himself, what was best for her.[%p]"

msgid "6900:妻の心が壊れる前に、“彼”の心が壊れてしまっていたのかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "6900:Perhaps his mind had broken before hers.[%p]"

msgid "7000:“彼”の目的はいつしか、ノアⅡの完成ではなく“妻に夢を見続けさせること”になっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "7000:And the more time passed, the more his goal changed from the completion of Noah II to keeping his wife locked within her dream.[%p]"

msgid "7100:そうして２年近く続けられた実験は、雇い主の言葉により唐突に終わりを告げた。[%p]"
msgstr "7100:And then, after almost two years, his employer's words suddenly brought all that to an end.[%p]"

msgid "7200:[name]野呂瀬[line]「データはじゅうぶん取れました。ノアⅡ本格稼働は間近です。この実験ももう続ける意味はないでしょう」[%p]"
msgstr "7200:[name]野呂瀬[line]We have enough data. Noah II will begin full operation soon. There's no point in continuing this experiment.[%p]"

msgid "7300:“彼”は必死で抵抗した。[linebreak]だがそれによって裏切り者の烙印を押され、プロジェクトから外された。[%p]"
msgstr "7300:He fought back as hard as he could. But as a result, he was branded a traitor, and removed from the project.[%p]"

msgid "7400:実験場が閉鎖される日、せめてもの温情として、彼は縛られたまま実験室への同席を許された。[%p]"
msgstr "7400:As a final thanks for his service, he was allowed to be in the experiment room, hands tied, on the day it was shut down.[%p]"

msgid "7500:そしてそこには、２年間顔も合わせていなかった長女もまた、同席させられていた。[%p]"
msgstr "7500:His daughter, whom he hadn't seen for nearly two years, had been brought there as well.[%p]"

msgid "7600:“彼”の姿を認めて、娘は戸惑いの表情を浮かべた。[%p]"
msgstr "7600:When she saw him, she seemed confused.[%p]"

msgid "7700:[name]セナ[line]「父さん！\u3000これはどういうこと？\u3000母さんに、なにをしたの？」[%p]"
msgstr "7700:[name]セナ[line]Dad! What's going on here? What did you do to Mom?[%p]"

msgid "7800:[name]セナ[line]「母さんが抱いているのは……いったい……」[%p]"
msgstr "7800:[name]セナ[line]What is she holding?[%p]"

msgid "7900:“彼”には答えられなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "7900:He couldn't answer.[%p]"

msgid "8000:自分のしていたことの後ろめたさで、娘の顔をまともに見られなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "8000:The guilt kept him from even looking her in the eye.[%p]"

msgid "8100:その間にも、凄惨なる儀式の始まりが迫っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "8100:The horrible ceremony was about to begin.[%p]"

msgid "8200:“婦人”はすでに、腐敗臭に耐えきれなくなっており、“家政婦”が妻の言葉に涙を流しながら、実験場を出た。[%p]"
msgstr "8200:The “neighbor lady” had already become unable to tolerate the stench. And the “maid” had run out of the lab weeping at his wife's words.[%p]"

msgid "8300:そして、装置は止められ、[linebreak]"
msgstr "8300:The device was shut down.[linebreak]"

msgid "8400:“夢”は終わり、[%p]"
msgstr "8400:The dream ended.[%p]"

msgid "8500:そして、装置は止められ、“夢”は終わり、[linebreak]"
msgstr "8500:The device was shut down. The dream ended.[linebreak]"

msgid "8600:妻は[unk07 unk="60"]壊れた。[%p]"
msgstr "8600:And his wife[unk07 unk="60"] broke.[%p]"

msgid "8700:突如ミイラと化した――[unk07 unk="60"]ように妻には見えただろう――[unk07 unk="60"]我が子の姿に、[unk07 unk="60"]自らの頭をかきむしり、[unk07 unk="60"]髪を引きちぎり、[unk07 unk="60"]顔面の皮膚を爪でえぐった[%p]"
msgstr "8700:At the sight of her daughter suddenly turning into a desiccated corpse—[unk07 unk="60"] at least, that's how it must've seemed to her—[unk07 unk="60"] she snapped,[unk07 unk="60"] tearing out her hair and ripping the skin off her face with her nails.[%p]"

msgid "8800:狂ったように笑い、"
msgstr "8800:She began to laugh, madly,"

msgid "8900:[unk07 unk="60"]頭を壁に打ち付け、[%p]"
msgstr "8900:[unk07 unk="60"] slamming her face again and again into the walls,[%p]"

msgid "9000:狂ったように笑い、頭を壁に打ち付け、"
msgstr "9000:She began to laugh, madly, slamming her face again and again into the walls,"

msgid "9100:やがて[unk07 unk="60"]包丁で"
msgstr "9100:before grabbing[unk07 unk="60"] a knife..."

msgid "9200:[unk07 unk="120"]自らの目をえぐって[unk07 unk="90"]死んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "9200:[unk07 unk="120"] and killing herself by stabbing out her own eyes.[%p]"

msgid "9300:やがて包丁で自らの目をえぐって死んだ。"
msgstr "9300:before grabbing a knife… and killing herself by stabbing out her own eyes."

msgid "9400:[name]セナ[line]「母さん！\u3000母さんっ！」[%p]"
msgstr "9400:[name]セナ[line]Mom! Mom![%p]"

msgid "9500:娘が、マジックミラーの向こうで母の無惨な最期を見て、泣き叫んでいた。[%p]"
msgstr "9500:Her daughter was screaming and crying as she watched her mother's last moments through the one-way mirror.[%p]"

msgid "9600:[name]セナ[line]「母さ……う、おおええ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "9600:[name]セナ[line]Mom... Waaah![%p]"

msgid "9700:[name]セナ[line]「う、うう、はあ、はあ、[linebreak]ああああ、ああああああ、母さん、かあさ……」[%p]"
msgstr "9700:[name]セナ[line]Hahh... Hahh... Aaah! Aaaaah! Mom![%p]"

msgid "9800:[name]セナ[line]「いやあああああああああああああああああ――！」[%p]"
msgstr "9800:[name]セナ[line]Aaaaaaaaaaah![%p]"

msgid "9900:そのまま、娘は研究員たちに両脇を抱えられ、いずこかへと連れられていった。“彼”には、残されたたったひとりの家族を追いかけることも許されなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "9900:The lab staff grabbed his daughter by the arms and dragged her off somewhere. He didn't know where. He wasn't even allowed to follow the only family he had left.[%p]"

msgid "10000:[name]波多野[line]「済まない……済まない……」[%p]"
msgstr "10000:[name]波多野[line]I'm sorry... I'm so sorry.[%p]"

msgid "10100:すべて自業自得だったのだと、“彼”は自らを責めた。[%p]"
msgstr "10100:He blamed himself. It was all his fault.[%p]"

msgid "10200:２年前に、理由はどうあれ“彼”が実験を続けることを決意したときから、こうなることは目に見えていたのだ。[%p]"
msgstr "10200:Whatever his reasons, when he'd opted to continue the experiment two years prior, it had been obvious that this was how it was going to end.[%p]"

msgid "10300:妻を看取った数日後、“彼”は姿を消した。[linebreak]今はどこにいるのか、誰も知らない。[%p]"
msgstr "10300:Several days after watching his wife's death, he disappeared. Nobody knew where he was now.[%p]"

